Title: Resumming the Effective Action
Authors: A. Leonidov, A. Zelnikov
Comments: 7 pages, BI-TP 93/38 (revised)
\\
  At the simple example of a massless scalar field propagating in the static
background we study the resummed expressions for the effective action at zero
and finite temperature that are free from a usual sickness of the effective
action induced by massless particles.
